{"tid":1452510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"#我是护旗手 你地班國賊唔好再dum國旗落海！","createTime":"2019-08-12T01:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T01:48:10.000Z","uid":194164,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a5ecefbb2dd4fed33eb1d89a36bd01ec653ae1d0","tid":1452510,"uid":194164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:32:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你地班暴徒做咩成日拆咗支國旗dum落海？知唔知咁樣會污染環境同好唔尊重國家？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我強烈要求你地學識<strong>愛國</strong>，去到邊都攬住支旗！偷國旗可恥，但浪費支旗仲可恥！每個星期進行<strong>舞旗巡遊</strong>咪唔會搞到煙霧瀰漫囉。年輕人要用腦先得㗎！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 《國旗及國徽條例》</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">7. 保護國旗、國徽<br />\n任何人公開及故意以焚燒、毀損、塗劃、玷污、踐踏等方式侮辱國旗或國徽，即屬犯罪，一經定罪，可處第5級罰款及監禁3年。</span></span>"},{"pid":"220ce112fa768a3b1ea7246da0ca8a10534b29ac","tid":1452510,"uid":194164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:47:10.000Z","msg":"負評前，請仔細閱讀"},{"pid":"e5ac922a334739eec0c226f8ea9c36970117699e","tid":1452510,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:47:57.000Z","msg":"[輸出革命］由今日起，不叫港獨，改叫「廣獨」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447204</a>"},{"pid":"8842c4322c40131d642a3ca01dafad152b6c142f","tid":1452510,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:48:10.000Z","msg":"拎黎抆屎做地布<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}